  "text": "The list of tractography parameters used for the FiberCup experiments is shown in Table 2 . The parameters are carefully chosen such that all techniques can successfully capture all the 7 bundles of the FiberCup phantom with low amount of false connections. However parameters are not optimized for any of the approaches. Because the elimination of the short streamlines can drastically change the results, we conducted two sets of evaluations addressing this issue. In one set, we did not remove any short tracks as adopted in [CITATION_1] . In another set, we removed the streamlines shorter than 20 mm which was adopted in [CITATION_2] . For the reconstruction of tractograms, we used the white matter mask provided with the phantom and uniformly seeded it to obtain 100 thousand streamlines for each technique. ",
